          <title>Muggers ripped watch off Dodgers pitcher Walker Buehler's arm, police say</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Police in California say thieves surrounded Los Angeles Dodgers starting pitcher Walker Buehler last month and ripped a pricey watch off his arm.   

Police say the victims were all targets of organized groups who steal high-end watches in large crowds during events.]]></description>
